** Beginning in 2024, all variables for "Non-Hispanic/Latina/e/o" "Hispanic/Latina/e/o" "American Indian, Alaska Native, or Indigenous" "Asian or Asian American" "Black, African American, or African" "Middle Eastern or North African" "Native Hawaiian, or Other Pacific Islander" "White" and "Multi-Racial" are aggregated based on the race/ethnicity combinations reported and are included for historical comparison purposes. These may not sum to the total because those who reported as Hispanic Only in 2024 are not included in the aggregated racial categories and the unsheltered data carried over from 2023 did not include these new race/ethnicity combinations.
